\c 5 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 5\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Geggeeffamuu Fi Eegamuu Warra Waaqayyoon Amanatanii (Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf, kun ululleedhaan faarfatame; faarfannaa Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, gurra kee gara dubbii kootti qabi, isa ani hasaasee sitti himadhus yaadatti anaaf fudhadhu.
\m \bd 2\bd* Ani sin kadhadha yaa mootii ko, yaa Waaqayyoo ko, sagalee iyya kootii dhaggeeffadhu!
\m \bd 3\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, ganama sagaleen koo si biratti in dhaga'ama, ganama ofii koo siif nan qopheessa, gara kees nan ilaala.
\m \bd 4\bd* Ati yaa Waaqayyo, isa jal'inni itti tolu miti'o, hamaanis si bira hin buufatu.
\m \bd 5\bd* Warri of jajanis ija kee dura hin dhaabatan, warra wanta waa'ee hin baafne hojjetan hundumaas in jibbita.
\m \bd 6\bd* Warra soba dubbatan lafa irraa in balleessita, Waaqayyo warra dhiiga namaa dhangalaasanii fi warra nama wallaalchisan in ciigga'a.
\m \bd 7\bd* Ani garuu gaarummaa kee isa baay'eedhaan gara mana keetti ol galuun anaaf kennameera; ulfinaan si sodaachuudhaanis, gara mana qulqullummaa keetti garagalee kufee siif nan sagada.
\m \bd 8\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, sababii warri adeemsa koo caqasan jiraniif, ati qajeelummaa keetiin na geggeessi! Karaa kees fuula koo duratti anaaf qajeelchi! 
\m \bd 9\bd* Afaan warra akkasii keessaa dubbiin dhaabataan hin ba'u, keessa mar'umaan isaanii badiisatu jira, afaan isaaniitiin gara awwaala banamaatti nama geessu, arraba dhadhaa dibatanii in dubbatu.
\m \bd 10\bd* Egaa isaan si irratti ka'aniiru, yaa Waaqayyo, yakkitoota ta'uu isaanii beeksisi! Isaan haa kufan, mareen isaaniis lafatti haa hafu! Baay'ina irra-daddarbaa isaaniitiif bakkeetti isaan gati!
\m \bd 11\bd* Warri kooluu sitti galan hundinuu garuu haa gammadan, bara baraanis haa ililchan! Ati warra maqaa kee jaallatan waan eegduuf; isaan sitti haa gammadan.
\m \bd 12\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, ati nama qajeelaa in eebbifta, tolli kees karaa hundumaa gaachana in ta'aaf.
\b 
